basic.description:
{Basic Navigation}

Basic Navigation increases the hero's movement over water by 50%.

It allows boarding and disembarking ships without ending the turn. When boarding or landing, the hero's remaining movement is converted between land and water movement.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Navigation}

Advanced Navigation increases the hero's movement over water by 100%.

It allows boarding and disembarking ships without ending the turn. When boarding or landing, the hero's remaining movement is converted between land and water movement.

